Author: jessusisabiscuit
Text: First of all, that's so awesome! I'm glad you're having a good experience and enjoying being good to your body! You should be proud and a little validation is not too much to ask.

Text: i’ve also been called ungrateful for having an eating disorder. i don’t understand why people act like it’s their problem. no mom i’m not doing this to get attention, can you leave me alone now
